@mterenzio I've been using Websockets pretty routinely these days.
The Instant Outlines feature supported by Drummer uses them. When you open one, it has a WS link back to the publisher, and when the outline updates, the updated is transmitted to the viewers.

@mterenzio Everything I've read about WS says that it's totally cool to rely on the tech, nothing experimental about it.
